scp instructions
http://blog.51cto.com/superw/1943250


copy file from local to server:
run on local terminal:
scp filename root@149.28.204.195:/route

copy file from server to local:
run on local terminal:
scp filename root@149.28.204.195:/route desire_route

copy all the files in the directory:
run on local terminal:
scp -r /route/ root@149.28.204.195:/



